.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art9.jpg&quot; class=&quot;cboxElement&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(192, 30, 34); text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter size-full wp-image-2166 box-hide box-show&quot; src=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art9.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;1080&quot; height=&quot;488&quot; title=&quot;应该怎样设计字体？各种「字的玩法」案例特搜 灵感创意 第9张-集优小站&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; transition: -webkit-transform 0.15s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.2s ease 0s, z-index 0.15s ease 0s;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;你相信上面的作品都是由文字「画」出来的么？&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;在字体公司森泽推出的Fontpark 网页上，你也可以试着用字画一幅画。这是一个简单黑白两色的Flash 平台，却展现出令人惊艳的效果。他们通过技术让文字游戏变得更加具有参与性，简单、有趣、激发&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.jiyoua.com/tag/%e7%81%b5%e6%84%9f&quot; title=&quot;【查看含有[灵感]标签的文章】&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(192, 30, 34); text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;灵感&lt;/a&gt;，又蕴藏着千变万化。&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art10.jpg&quot; class=&quot;cboxElement&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(192, 30, 34); text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter size-full wp-image-2167 box-hide box-show&quot; src=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art10.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;1044&quot; height=&quot;753&quot; title=&quot;应该怎样设计字体？各种「字的玩法」案例特搜 灵感创意 第10张-集优小站&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; transition: -webkit-transform 0.15s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.2s ease 0s, z-index 0.15s ease 0s;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;用平假名画出的舞い姫&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;在这里，你可以输入任意汉字，选择字体，将它们拆解成部分，或是单独的笔划，通过放大、缩小、位移、扭曲、翻转等等手段，组合拼装，只要有无限的想像力，画出什么样的作品就看你了。&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art11.jpg&quot; class=&quot;cboxElement&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(192, 30, 34); text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter size-full wp-image-2168 box-hide box-show&quot; src=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art11.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;566&quot; height=&quot;328&quot; title=&quot;应该怎样设计字体？各种「字的玩法」案例特搜 灵感创意 第11张-集优小站&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; transition: -webkit-transform 0.15s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.2s ease 0s, z-index 0.15s ease 0s;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art12.jpg&quot; class=&quot;cboxElement&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(192, 30, 34); text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter size-full wp-image-2169 box-hide box-show&quot; src=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art12.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;566&quot; height=&quot;328&quot; title=&quot;应该怎样设计字体？各种「字的玩法」案例特搜 灵感创意 第12张-集优小站&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; transition: -webkit-transform 0.15s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.2s ease 0s, z-index 0.15s ease 0s;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;网站上网友自发创作的作品&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;为了让你也能玩好这个文字游戏，Voicer 贴心制作了操作攻略：&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;-输入汉字（注意需要是日文字体），点选后出现在画面上&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;-触发汉字，选择你需要的笔划拖出&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;-移动/旋转：鼠标点击拖动&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;-放大/缩小：鼠标滚轮或键盘上下键&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;-复制：双击&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;-成组：鼠标拖动框选&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;-删除：移动文字扔出画面&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h2 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 5px 0px 5px 24px; outline: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 6px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: solid; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-image: initial; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 1.8rem; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 35px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; text-align: center;\'&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-family: inherit;&quot;&gt;地铁上的一个字礼仪&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;&quot;&gt;2016 东京地铁海报&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art13.jpg&quot; class=&quot;cboxElement&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(192, 30, 34); text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter size-full wp-image-2170 box-hide box-show&quot; src=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art13.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;1080&quot; height=&quot;509&quot; title=&quot;应该怎样设计字体？各种「字的玩法」案例特搜 灵感创意 第13张-集优小站&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; transition: -webkit-transform 0.15s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.2s ease 0s, z-index 0.15s ease 0s;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;「红灯闪烁请勿冲门」，「先下后上」，「友爱让座」……这些常见的地铁礼仪，被东京地下铁设计成了「一个汉字」的海报。也许你已经觉得日本人在地铁上够有规矩了，还需要强调搭车的礼仪吗？其实，良好的习惯正是来源于长期的培养。&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;东京地铁从1974 年开始，在每一年4 月到下一年3 月，都会推出一整套设计水准极高的海报，每月更新，佳作不断。近几年，还和年轻人中备受欢迎的插画家如文平银座、冈村优太等合作，削减了海报的说教意味，风格更加温馨有趣。&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art14.jpg&quot; class=&quot;cboxElement&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(192, 30, 34); text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter size-full wp-image-2171 box-hide box-show&quot; src=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art14.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;637&quot; title=&quot;应该怎样设计字体？各种「字的玩法」案例特搜 灵感创意 第14张-集优小站&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; transition: -webkit-transform 0.15s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.2s ease 0s, z-index 0.15s ease 0s;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;「扉」，门全开后，请先下后上&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art15.jpg&quot; class=&quot;cboxElement&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(192, 30, 34); text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter size-full wp-image-2172 box-hide box-show&quot; src=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art15.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;637&quot; title=&quot;应该怎样设计字体？各种「字的玩法」案例特搜 灵感创意 第15张-集优小站&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; transition: -webkit-transform 0.15s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.2s ease 0s, z-index 0.15s ease 0s;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;「见」，请注意，不要边走边看手机&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;2016 年的主题正是「汉字」。东京地铁邀请了这几年非常有人气的插画家长场雄，为每一种礼仪画了简洁的图示，让人一眼就能明白海报的意思。其中，有几张海报宣导的「礼仪」，也让我们非常有共鸣。比如：&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art16.jpg&quot; class=&quot;cboxElement&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(192, 30, 34); text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter size-full wp-image-2173 box-hide box-show&quot; src=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art16.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;637&quot; title=&quot;应该怎样设计字体？各种「字的玩法」案例特搜 灵感创意 第16张-集优小站&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; transition: -webkit-transform 0.15s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.2s ease 0s, z-index 0.15s ease 0s;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;「滴」，雨天，要注意雨伞滴水&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Tahoma, sans-serif; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Word-Art17.jpg&quot; class=&quot;cboxElement&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(192, 30, 34); text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter size-full wp-image-2174 box-hide box-show&quot; src=&quot;https://jiyoua-1251995454.cosgz.myqcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/W